Adverse Events Log

Source: R/data.R
ADVERSE.Rd

Adverse Events Log data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(ADVERSE)

Format

A data frame with 3405 observations and 89 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNIGO, ADNI3, ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI4

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with factor levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 10436

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • AENUMBER numeric Adverse event number Range value: 1, ..., 34

  • AECHANGE character Is this event a:

    • ADNI3: 1=New adverse event;2=Worsening condition or symptom present at screening/initial visit

    • ADNI4: 1=New adverse event; 2=Worsening condition or symptom present at screening/initial visit

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEPENUM numeric Initial Health Assessment Condition Number: Range value: 0, ..., 59

  • AECOMPOUND character Is this event part of a compound event?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHONSDT Date Event onset date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEOUTCOME character Event outcome

    • ADNI3: 1=Recovered/Resolved;2=Recovering/Resolving;3=Not recovered/Not resolved;4=Recovered/Resolved with sequelae;5=Fatal;6=Unknown

    • ADNI4: 1=Recovered/Resolved; 2=Recovering/Resolving; 3=Not recovered/Not resolved; 4=Recovered/Resolved with sequelae; 5=Fatal; 6=Unknown

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCSDT Date Event cease date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEHDTHDT numeric Date of death Range value: 2017, ..., 2025

  • AEHDBRN character Was a brain autopsy performed? 0=No;1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCHRON character Initial Chronicity

    • ADNI3: 1=Single occurrence;2=Intermittent - daily;3=Intermittent - weekly;4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently;5=Persistent

    • ADNI4: 1=Single occurrence; 2=Intermittent - daily; 3=Intermittent - weekly; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently; 5=Persistent

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHSEVR character Initial Severity

    • ADNI3: 1=Mild;2=Moderate;3=Severe

    • ADNI4: 1=Mild; 2=Moderate; 3=Severe

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELAD character Related to symptoms associated with the development of early stage AD or progression of AD

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELCM character Related to concomitant therapy

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELFLRBTBN character Related to Florbetaben tracer

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELFLRBPR character Related to Florbetapir tracer

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHIMG character Related to PET/MRI imaging procedure

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELTAU character Related to Flotaucipir tracer

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELNAV character Related to NAV-4694 tracer 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELMK character Related to MK-6240 tracer 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELPI character Related to PI-2620 tracer 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHLUMB character Related to lumbar puncture

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELCOVID character Related to COVID-19 illness

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely (Confirmed COVID-19 test);2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely (Confirmed COVID-19 test); 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELPAN character Related to COVID-19 pandemic disruption

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELATESP character Related to other study procedure(s)

    • ADNI3: 1=Definitely;2=Probably;3=Possibly;4=Unlikely;5=Not related

    • ADNI4: 1=Definitely; 2=Probably; 3=Possibly; 4=Unlikely; 5=Not related

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCMEDS character Was treatment (medication) for AE required?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AESERIOUS character Was event serious at any time during the trial?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AESERDATE Date Date event became serious: Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEDTSITE Date Date site became aware that the event is serious: Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SAELIFE character Is this an SAE because event was life-threatening?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEHOSPIT character Is this an SAE because it lead to hospitalization?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEPROLONG character Is this an SAE because it lead to prolongation of hospitalization?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEDEATH character Is this an SAE because it lead to death?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAECONGEN character Is this an SAE because it lead to a congenital anomaly or birth defect?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEDISAB character Is this an SAE because it caused persistent or significant disability/incapacity?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEOTHER character Is this an SAE because it lead to another medically important condition?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE1 character Is there a change to report?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE1 Date Change 1. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV1 character Change 1: Severity

    • ADNI3: 1=Mild;2=Moderate;3=Severe

    • ADNI4: 1=Mild; 2=Moderate; 3=Severe

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON1 character Change 1: Chronicity

    • ADNI3: 1=Single occurrence;2=Intermittent - daily;3=Intermittent - weekly;4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently;5=Persistent

    • ADNI4: 1=Single occurrence; 2=Intermittent - daily; 3=Intermittent - weekly; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently; 5=Persistent

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE2 character Is there a 2nd change to report?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE2 Date Change 2. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV2 character Change 2: Severity

    • ADNI3: 1=Mild;2=Moderate;3=Severe

    • ADNI4: 1=Mild; 2=Moderate; 3=Severe

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON2 character Change 2: Chronicity

    • ADNI3: 1=Single occurrence;2=Intermittent - daily;3=Intermittent - weekly;4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently;5=Persistent

    • ADNI4: 1=Single occurrence; 2=Intermittent - daily; 3=Intermittent - weekly; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently; 5=Persistent

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE3 numeric Is there a 3rd change to report?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

  • AEDATE3 logical Change 3. Date Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV3 logical Change 3: Severity

    • ADNI3: 1=Mild;2=Moderate;3=Severe

    • ADNI4: 1=Mild; 2=Moderate; 3=Severe

  • AECHRON3 logical Change 3: Chronicity

    • ADNI3: 1=Single occurrence;2=Intermittent - daily;3=Intermittent - weekly;4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently;5=Persistent

    • ADNI4: 1=Single occurrence; 2=Intermittent - daily; 3=Intermittent - weekly; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently; 5=Persistent

  • AECHANGE4 logical Is there a 4th change to report?

    • ADNI3: 0=No;1=Yes

    • ADNI4: 0=No; 1=Yes

  • AEDATE4 logical Change 4. Date Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV4 logical Change 4: Severity

    • ADNI3: 1=Mild;2=Moderate;3=Severe

    • ADNI4: 1=Mild; 2=Moderate; 3=Severe

  • AECHRON4 logical Change 4: Chronicity
